<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure125>
    dc:description "Figure 125. Solanum pilcomayense A flowering and fruiting habit B eglandular leaf trichome C calyx D glandular trichome of the calyx E flower F dissected flower G eglandular trichome of the corolla H stamen, dorsal view I stamen, ventral view J gynoeciu K frui L fruit, longitudinal section M seed N seed, longitudinal section (A-N Barboza et al. 2287). Illustration by P. Peralta. Previously published in Barboza et al. (2013: 254)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897586" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure126>
    dc:description "Figure 126. Solanum pilcomayense A habit (live plant) B habit (herbarium sheet) C inflorescences with buds D flowers at full anthesis E fruiting branch with maturing fruits (A Pena-Chocarro et al. 1496 B-D Rojas 108 [G 00306746] E Morong 898 [PH 00030470]). Reproduced with permission of the Conservatoire et Jardins Botaniques de la Ville de Geneve and the Philadelphia Academy of Sciences (Drexel University)." ;
